Description: Software package assistant
 This is Anvil, a software package assistant:
 .
 - It features repository filters handling whitespace and encodings.
 - It features a sed-based respoitory filter.
 - It features a nice pre-commit hook enforcing whitespace
   and filename policies.
 - It features an elementary git releng command.
